v8:item.v8:content: [SNP], hereinafter in this agreement referred to as "Personal Data Subject" granted to the [Company], on behalf of responsible of personal data processing [ResponsibleForPersonalDataProcessing] hereinafter "Operator", the right to process personal data, as described in paragraf 2 of the present agreement, under the following conditions:

1. The owner of personal data gives his consent to process his personal data by the operator for the purposes as follows: collection, systematization, acquiring, storage, clarification (update, modification), usage, distribution (including transfer), depersonalization, locking, deletion of personal data, at that the above mentioned methods of data processing are described by the Federal Law from 27.07.2006 No. 152-FZ "On personal data" for the purposes as follows: - to fulfil the obligations under labour agreement; - to ensure employee's safety, security and health; - to maintain business activity of the company; - other (specify exact purpose).

2. The list of personal data provided to the operator for processing (underline as appropriate): - date and place of birth; - biography; - education (educational organization, period of education, qualification); - employments data (city, company, position, work period); - martial status, children (surname, name, patronymic, date of birth); - place of registration, residence; - contact information; - passport data; - taxpayer data (TIN); - pension fund registration data (INILA); - valid bank accounts; - other (specify exact data).

3. IN accordance with paragraph 4 of Item 14 of the Federal Law from 27.07.2006 No. 152-FZ "On personal data" the owner of the personal data has a right to retreive the information related to the processing of his personal data upon written request.

5. The operator has a right to process the personal data for the purposes as follows (underline as appropriate): - collection; - systematization; - acquisition; - storage; - clarification (update, modification); - usage; - distribution/transfer; - locking; - deletion; - other (specify exact purpose).
6. Agreement can be revoked by me at any time according to my letter of application.
Responsible for the personal data processing
